{"tid":584363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸之後","createTime":"2018-03-07T18:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:34:16.000Z","uid":62324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"643ec90ec253f9ff4ea9518973acbe5556f7eda2","tid":584363,"uid":62324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:37:17.000Z","msg":"好多人講食完A酸之後，皮膚真係好左。呢樣係真既，皮膚好左既意思係塊面既所有暗瘡都會3個月內消失。<br />\n<br />\n當然，A酸係有用，但係唔係仙丹囉。食完唔會變到李嘉欣咁皮膚零瑕疵。而我正正就係因為咁而開Post。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無聽過酒糟鼻? 我正正就係有呢樣野。唔知係咩黎既話，巴絲上網Google下應該知嫁啦。而家食完A酸就要執手尾，諗住整返平個鼻上面既多餘組織。<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想要返個普普通通既鼻見人。希望有身同感受既巴絲幫下我，比小小建議我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1194e08013451bd0c9fc2221508bc8e11c749288","tid":584363,"uid":8867,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0edf8d1a05265397db5605e2905e0ab056b305eb","tid":584363,"uid":62324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1194e08013451bd0c9fc2221508bc8e11c749288","tid":584363,"uid":8867,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"右咩啊右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e156b73d4bed8ef241872f5e9972a48e879b8def","tid":584363,"uid":62324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"都話左皮膚會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗返起之前d戇尻親戚話唔好食咁多M記，真係笑左! 暗瘡係由荷爾蒙直接導致，所以塊面係會局部生。 就算我食M記，都可能只食1生2至3粒暗瘡。"},{"pid":"6c5c26347f17f35e62deb69a80608548a3e7f7a5","tid":584363,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:51:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7024d8391c257da058247a7aad2f119beabfd45","tid":584363,"uid":14963,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6c5c26347f17f35e62deb69a80608548a3e7f7a5","tid":584363,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e156b73d4b